
## Manual Test Checklist

1. Open app via local server.
2. Confirm default route becomes `#/home`.
3. Visit all routes:
   - `#/home`
   - `#/dashboard`
   - `#/calculator`
   - `#/workflow`
   - `#/contact`
4. Resize to mobile and verify hamburger behavior.
5. Dashboard counters animate, chart moves, logs update.
6. Navigate away from dashboard and confirm old timers stop.
7. Calculator sliders/model update totals and bars.
8. Reload and confirm calculator values persist.
9. Workflow SVG nodes update the detail card by click and keyboard.
10. FAQ search filters entries.
11. Copy command button writes the run command and shows toast.
12. Contact empty submit shows validation errors.
13. Invalid email is rejected.
14. Valid contact submit shows spinner then success toast.
15. Skip link and focus rings work.
16. Reload once, set browser offline, refresh, confirm cached shell loads.

## Notes

- No npm dependencies.
- No build step.
- No Tailwind or chart libraries.
- No secrets.
- No backend/API submission.
